sentences: Ayana Taketatsu (竹達 彩奈, Taketatsu Ayana, born June 23, 1989) is a Japanese voice actress and singer.
She is now affiliated with Link Plan.
In 2013, Taketatsu formed a singing unit, Petit Milady, with Aoi Yūki.
On January 3, 2017, Taketatsu announced on her blog that she left the talent agency Assemble Heart for the agency Link Plan on January 1.
On June 23, 2019, Taketatsu announced on Twitter that she had married Yuki Kaji on her birthday.
